summary: When Hoseok gets Jealous  Seokjin • Yoongi • Hoseok • Namjoon • Jimin • Taehyung • Jungkook   Drunk Hoseok and Jealous Hoseok...
body:
When Hoseok gets Jealous

Seokjin • Yoongi • Hoseok • Namjoon • Jimin • Taehyung • Jungkook

  • Drunk Hoseok and Jealous Hoseok aren’t that different
  • The second he feels that green little monster coming up he shuts down
  • Looks like he regrets his whole existence
  • Turns an odd red color
  • Actually looks like he wants to get hit by a truck
  • Quiet as all hell
  • Watches quietly
  • Dead ass this man looks like he’s about to cry and puke at the same time
  • Which is what catches your attention
  • “Baby you okay? You don’t look so good.”
  • “I’m fine.”
  • Clearly he isn’t
  • You brush the guy you were having a conversation with off and turn your full attention to your boyfriend
  • He just looks at you as if he is looking through you
  • Seriously is he okay?
  • It’s like he’s running on autopilot
  • Finally he explains himself in a monotone voice
  • You shower him in affection telling him nothing is wrong and nothing would happen
  • Comes to life a little more only to act like a kicked puppy with water eyes
  • Again you shower him in affection and assure him you are his and his alone
  • Sinks into your embrace like I tired kid and refuses to let you go (despite you being the one to hold him)
